  <brief_title>Effect of Hypnotherapy in Irritable Bowel Syndrome (IBS)</brief_title>
  <official_title>Effectiviteit Van Hypnotherapie Bij Prikkelbare Darmsyndroom (Effectiveness of Hypnotherapy in Irritable Bowel Syndrome)</official_title>
