  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      In this trial, the effects of two psychological interventions - i.e. hypnotherapy and
      relaxation training - are compared with care as usual in IBS treatment. The investigators
      hypothesized that hypnotherapy is most effective in reducing complaints in IBS.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
